{"tid":2401070,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍播新宣傳片 大讚95KG駐港新兵4月減40斤：勵志","createTime":"2021-02-09T12:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T12:23:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"df9bad4fbf39dbc14727df3a5cd9cfbd923362c3","tid":2401070,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:22:37.000Z","msg":"解放軍播新宣傳片 大讚95KG駐港新兵4月減40斤：勵志<br />\nFeb 9, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oQ-07mG9O9I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoQ-07mG9O9I&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQmVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=ba2bc47c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oQ-07mG9O9I</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n57.5K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n央視軍事頻道周一晚上，在微博上載新的宣傳片，講述了幾個新兵入伍的故事。其中一個是駐港部隊的新兵，片段指他曾是「一個190斤的大胖子，入伍4個月，減掉了40斤。」帖文就指他的經歷勵志，要為他加油。<br />\n<br />\n不過在軍方出力宣傳之際，多地都傳出有新兵入伍後，拒服兵役而被除名處分。"},{"pid":"e4666cd3f93a56dfbf148cfd89c88c58657eb9ef","tid":2401070,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}